{
  "stem": "5371.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, I know how to converse with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I speak Hebrew, and I could-- and I could tell them what to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Just tell me what you want them to do, and I tell them what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And why should they be beaten and kicked, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they don't understand the language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They don't understand what they were told to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, OK, because he was in charge there too, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a big say in the place there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I explained to them in Hebrew, because not all of them spoke Hebrew, but a few of them spoke Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were a few young men there and a couple older men also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they-- after we finished the building-- not completely finished, but after we did most of the cement work-- they put them up to do the windows, to clean the windows.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they did clean the windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they put them in our own-- in, in my block, there on my, on my room there where I was, that big room, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Saturdays-- on Sundays-- we didn't work on Sundays-- on Sundays, they'd come over to me, and they brought me their portions of bread, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told them not to give it to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I says, I don't want it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, because you need it, because, you know, if you want to survive, you'll need that and much more, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were so grateful to me, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were kissing me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then after a while, you know, we were transferred to Birkenau, and I never heard from them anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened to them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
